_sText:
Map Name: Ka_Kyanite
Version: 1.0

Description: This is a sort of remake for the well known fy_kyanite which included guns. However according to ]HeLL[ Server votes,
everybody prefers the map as being knife only with sv_gravity 150. The textures in Fy_Kyanite were extremely poor. But have been upgraded
in this map. The grass even makes noise...
Make sure you set Sv_Gravity and Knifes Only whilst playing this map using your servers MANI ADMIN.
Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!
www.hellclan.co.uk
